products.body_html:
Transform your special occasion into a magical celebration with our Pink Butterfly Flower Fairy Theme Disposable Tableware! Perfect for girls' birthday parties, weddings, and baby showers, this enchanting set will add a whimsical touch to your decor. Each piece features delightful designs of butterflies and flowers, creating a charming atmosphere that will captivate your guests.


This complete tableware set includes beautifully designed plates, cups, and napkins, all made from high-quality paper that is both durable and environmentally friendly. With no high-concerned chemicals used in production, you can enjoy your party worry-free. The vibrant pink hues and intricate butterfly motifs are sure to delight children and adults alike, making every meal a feast for the eyes.

Feedback:

  1. We value your satisfaction! Please leave 5-star feedback if you're pleased with our products and service (Item as Described 5 stars, Communication 5 stars, Shipping time 5-stars).
    2. If you receive a damaged item or the wrong styles, please contact us before leaving negative feedback. We are committed to resolving any issues and ensuring your satisfaction.

Shipping and return policy:

1. Orders are typically processed within 24 hours of payment receipt.
2. Standard shipping via China post ordinary small packet plus and registered air mail takes approximately 15-60 days.
3. For a more stable, safer, and faster option, we recommend Aliexpress standard shipping.
4. We also offer express shipping options like DHL, UPS, and EMS for urgent orders or large quantities—just reach out to us for assistance!
5. Returns and refunds are accepted within 15 days after the order is completed; please contact us for support.

Dropshipping and wholesale:

1. We provide dropshipping services worldwide; feel free to contact us with any questions or concerns.
2. For wholesale inquiries, we offer competitive pricing and will recommend the best shipping options available.
